5182  CallRuntime(Runtime::kCopyDataProperties, context, result, source);
5183  Return(result);
5184 
5185  // Final fallback is to call into the runtime version.
5186  BIND(&call_runtime);
5187  Return(CallRuntime(Runtime::kCloneObjectIC_Slow, context, source, flags));
5188 }
